Kingfish Grill was established in June 2005 by owner Paul Mackey. Originally from coastal New England, the restaurateur has a passion for seafood, using his background & upbringing to contribute to the flare and spice at Kingfish Grill. The team at Kingfish Grill have made it a favorite restaurant among locals and visitors alike.
